          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E4* Istanbul hotel\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWelcome dinner included\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAll guided tours, excursions \u0026amp; entrance fees included\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELunch included on Day 3\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECruise on Day 3 included\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EReturn UK airport coach transfers\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDirect Turkish Airlines flights from London to Istanbul\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EProfessional local guide for all transfers \u0026amp; included day excursions\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EExecutive coach throughout\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAudio headsets included on Days 2 to 4\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "1d09b5af-b95a-4af5-b8f2-323db029e817",
      "key": "e4bd4d9f-8f10-4154-96c5-8910eeee0a0e",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Accommodation"
        },
        {
          "alias": "richTextContent",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe stay four nights at the 4* Barcelo Hotel (\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.barcelo.com/en-gb/barcelo-\u0022\u003Ewww.barcelo.com/en-gb/barcelo-\u003C/a\u003E istanbul/) at Istanbul. Located at Taksim Square, facilities at the hotel include a restaurant and bar. All rooms are en suite and feature television, hairdryer, and tea \u0026amp; coffee making facilities. A welcome set three course dinner without drinks is included at our hotel on the first evening, and the remaining three nights are on a bed and breakfast basis.\u003C/p\u003E\n"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
